            <title>[LU-5989] add subdirectory mounting support for lustre</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5989</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We might need subdirectory export for Lustre, just like NFS, we could use&lt;br/&gt;
it from clients something like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mount -t lustre xxxxx -o subdir=&quot;/test_dir&quot; &amp;lt;mnt&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Actually, we could implement it using a recursive way, we filter out mount options so that second mount will stop.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
